<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">  
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"> 
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>登录</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/signIn.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/common.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="libs/layui/lay/modules/layer.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="js/common.js"></script>
    <script src="js/signIn.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        ! function () {
            var html = document.documentElement;
            var hWidth = html.getBoundingClientRect().width;
            html.style.fontSize = hWidth / 15 + 'px';
        }();
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrap">
        <div class="header clearfix">
                <h2>登录</h2>
            <div class="passwordLogin">
                <p class="active">密码登录</p>
                <span class="active"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="phoneLogin">
                <p>手机号登录</p>
                <span></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="passwordTab ">
            <label for="passwordTab-Mobile">
                <span class="inpTel">手机号码</span>
                <input id="passwordTab-Mobile" type="tel" name="passwordTab-Mobile" data-attribute="请填写正确的手机号码" placeholder="请输入手机号码" maxlength="11">
            </label>
            <label for="resumePassword">
                <span class="password">密码</span>
                <input id="resumePassword" type="password" name="resumePassword" data-attribute="请填写密码" placeholder="请填写密码" maxlength="11">
            </label>
        </div>
        <div class="phoneTab active">
            <label for="phoneTab-Mobile">
                <span class="inpTel">手机号码</span>
                <input id="phoneTab-Mobile" type="tel" name="phoneTab-Mobile" data-attribute="请填写正确的手机号码" placeholder="请输入手机号码" maxlength="11">
            </label>
            <label for="validateCode" id="mesCodeLabel">
                <span class="msCode">验证码</span>
                <input id="validateCode"  type="text" name="validateCode" data-attribute="请填写正确的验证码" placeholder="请输入6位验证码" maxlength="6">
            <button type="button" id="mesBtn" class="mesBtn">获取验证码</button><br>

            </label>
        </div>
        <div class="agreementWrap">
            <span class="checkS">
                <input type="checkbox" class="input_check" id="check1" checked="checked">
                <label for="check1"></label>
            </span>
            <span class="read">我已阅读并同意</span>
            <span class="agreement">《易职信免责协议》</span>
        </div>
        <div class="login">
            <button>登录</button>
        </div>
        <div class="passwordTab-footer clearfix ">
            <div class="footerLeft">
                <span>还没有账号?</span>
                <span class="goRegister">去注册</span>
            </div>
            <div class="footerRight">
                <span>忘记密码?</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="phoneTab-footer clearfix active">
            <span>无法获取验证码</span>
        </div>

        <div class="codeExplain">
            <h2>无法获取验证码</h2>
            <h3>你可以尝试下列方式解决:</h3>
            <p>1、短信可以有2-10分钟延迟，可以稍等一下。</p>
            <p>2、查看是否误设短信拦截。</p>
            <p>3、确认手机缴费且服务正常。</p>
            <p>4、联系手机号运营商解除黑名单。</p>
            <div class="tel">
                <p>如以上无法解决，</p>
                <p>请拨打<span> 010-52830585 </span>获取帮助</p>
            </div>
            <div class="close">
                <img src="images/close.png" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footerTab">
        <p>
            <img src="images/index_sel.png" alt="">
            <a class="active" href="index.html">首页</a>
        </p>
        <p>
            <img src="images/report_pre.png" alt="">
            <a href="reportList.html">报告</a>
        </p>
        <p>
            <img src="images/my-pre.png" alt="">
            <a href="personal.html">我的</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>